headline: Will Prologis' (PLD) Energy Resilience Push and GROUNDBREAKERS Forum Shift Its Investment Narrative?
summary: In September and October 2025, Prologis, Inc. completed a US$1.17 billion dual-tranche notes offering, hosted its annual GROUNDBREAKERS forum in Los Angeles, and released a global survey highlighting growing concerns among supply chain managers about energy reliability in warehouses.
